title: TEMPLATE - July 17, 2013 (Week 14) PDF Edition
description:
Week 14 of TEMPLATE, a new digital comic series.
 
To catch up on the rest of the series for free, check out QAMCOMICS.COM

Do you like TEMPLATE and want to support the creative team? Now you can! Each month, we be collect high-resolution versions of the last four weeks of content and releasing them on the Comics Plus app for just $0.99 each. In addition to the visual bump and reading the story as originally intended, will also be adding some digital exclusives like inked art, script excerpts and other bonus items that will add to the experience.

QAM Comics on Comics Plus - http://digital.comicsplusapp.com/group_comics.php?publisher_id=149
